# ResumeDoctor Project Rules

## Project Context
Zety-style resume/CV builder SaaS. India-first, freemium model. Domain: resumedoctor.in. Tech: Next.js 14, React, TypeScript, Prisma, PostgreSQL, Tailwind, Stripe, OpenAI.

## Agent Workflow
- Read `AGENTS.md` and `docs/PRD-ROLE-BASED.md` before starting.
- Identify your role (Frontend/Backend/DevOps/Design/Content) and relevant WBS tasks.
- Reference `docs/WBS-WORK-BREAKDOWN-STRUCTURE.md` for task details and dependencies.
- Use kebab-case for file names. Follow existing folder structure.

## Key Paths
- App: `src/app/`
- Components: `src/components/`
- API: `src/app/api/`
- DB: `prisma/`
- Templates: `src/templates/` or `public/templates/`
- Docs: `docs/`

## Before Editing
- Check for existing similar code to avoid duplication.
- Ensure API routes validate input (Zod) and check auth.
- Use prepared statements / Prisma for DB (no raw SQL injection risks).
